Motion Pattern Analysis
=======================

This library was written as a part of my bachelors thesis and
implements the method detailed in the following paper:

Tool support for detection and analysis of following and
leadership behavior of pedestrians from mobile sensing data
	Mikkel Baun Kj√¶rgaard, Henrik Blunck, 2013

http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.pmcj.2013.10.007

Building
--------

Requirements:
	- CMake
	- Boost C++ Libraries 
	- G++ compiler with c++14 support, i.e. ~4.9 and later

To compile, run the following commands:

    $ mkdir build && cd build
    $ cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
    $ make -j5


